## Components Built

### `TileCta` вЂ” `src/components/TileCta/`
- **Figma**: "IconButtons/SrpTile"
- **Props**: `label?: string`, `href?: string`, `target?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Slots**: `#icon` (leading 24Г—24 SVG), default (label text)
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]`
- **Renders as**: `<button>` by default; `<a>` when `href` is provided
- **Dimensions**: height 40px, `border-radius: var(--border-radius-pill)`, gap 8px, padding 0 12px
- **Color scheme**: Accent (blue) вЂ” NOT primary green
- **Base**: `border: 3px solid transparent` (space reserved) + `box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px --color-accent-40` for layout-stable 2px border
- **States**: default=Accent40 2px border, hover=Accent30 3px border+text, active=Accent40 3px border+Accent90 bg, focus=Accessibility80 3px border, disabled=SecondaryNeutral90 bg+Neutral70 text
- **Icon colour**: `.tile-cta__icon :deep(path/circle/rect/polygon) { fill: currentColor }` вЂ” inherits all state colour changes automatically
- **Stories**: Default, Hover, Active, Focus, Disabled, AsAnchor, NoIcon, AllStates

### `IconButton` вЂ” `src/components/IconButton/`
- **Figma**: "IconButtons/SignIn"
- **Props**: `label?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Slots**: `#icon` (leading 24Г—24 SVG вЂ” import from `@icons/` using `?component`), default (label text)
- **Icon colour**: `.icon-button__icon :deep(path/circle/rect/polygon) { fill: currentColor }` in scoped CSS ensures the slotted SVG inherits the button colour automatically
- **Always**: small (40px), primary green вЂ” no variant/size/theme props
- **Layout**: `gap: 8px`, `padding: 4px 16px`, `border-radius: var(--border-radius-pill)`
- **States**: default=Primary50, hover=Primary40+underline, pressed=Primary55, focus=3px Accessibility80 border, disabled=SecondaryNeutral90 bg + Neutral70 text
- **Focus**: `border: 3px solid transparent` base, `border-color: --color-accessibility-80` on focus-visible (same overflow-clip technique as BaseButton primary)
- **Key tokens**: `--color-base-primary-40/50/55`, `--color-accessibility-80`, `--color-neutral-secondary-90`, `--color-neutral-70/100`
- **Stories**: Default, Hover, Active, Focus, Disabled, NoIcon, AllStates

### `LinkCta` вЂ” `src/components/LinkCta/`
- **Figma**: "CommonInputs/TextLink" (light), "CommonInputs/TextLink Dark" (dark)
- **Props**: `label?: string`, `arrow?: boolean` (default `false`), `theme?: 'light' | 'dark'` (default `'light'`), `href?: string`, `target?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]`
- **Renders as**: `<button>` by default; `<a>` when `href` is provided
- **Light states**: default/hover/focus = Accent40; pressed = Accent30; hover/pressed add underline
- **Dark states**: default/hover/focus = Accent80; pressed = Accent90; hover/pressed add underline
- **Focus ring**: 3px solid Accessibility80, outline-offset 2px, border-radius 2px (rectangular per Figma)
- **Disabled**: opacity `--opacity-level-medium` (32%), pointer-events none
- **Arrow icon**: imported from `@icons/Style=Arrows, Detail=No-Tail, Icon=Right.svg?component` вЂ” `.link-cta__arrow :deep(path) { fill: currentColor }` makes it inherit the link colour
- **Stories**: full LightГ—arrowГ—state + DarkГ—arrowГ—state coverage + AsAnchor + AllVariants
- **Key tokens**: `--color-accent-30/40/80/90`, `--color-accessibility-80`, `--opacity-level-medium`, `--font-*-btn`

### `BaseButton` вЂ” `src/components/BaseButton/`
- **Figma**: "Buttons/Primary" (primary md), "Buttons/Tertiary" (primary sm), "Buttons/Secondary" (secondary light md), "Buttons/TertiaryOutlined" (secondary light sm), "Buttons/SecondaryDark" (secondary dark md), "Buttons/TertiaryDark" (secondary dark sm)
- **Props**: `variant?: 'primary' | 'secondary'`, `size?: 'md' | 'sm'`, `theme?: 'light' | 'dark'`, `label?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]`
- **Sizes**: `md` = 56px h, 16px text; `sm` = 40px h, 14px text. All sizes work with all variants/themes.
- **Primary states**: hover (darker bg + underline), active (bright green), focus-visible (accessibility blue ring), disabled (grey). Theme prop has no effect.
- **Secondary light states**: hover (border thinв†’thick), active (thick border + neutral-95 fill), focus-visible (thick accessibility-blue border), disabled (grey bg)
- **Secondary dark states**: same border behaviour but white border/text; active fills with neutral-0 (dark); used on dark backgrounds
- **Stories**: full coverage of variantГ—sizeГ—themeГ—state + VariantComparison, SizeComparison, AllVariants. Dark stories use `backgrounds: { default: 'dark' }` parameter.
- **Storybook backgrounds**: light (#FFFFFF), dark (#242C33), neutral-95 (#F4F5F7) вЂ” registered in preview.ts
- **Key tokens used**: `--color-base-primary-*`, `--color-neutral-0/95/100`, `--color-accessibility-80`, `--border-radius-pill`, `--border-width-thin/thick`, `--font-*-btn*`

